            "answer_text": "Probably because they trigger a memory associated with the song and that song was a song you listened to or heard during a painful or fearful time in your past. The memory could be conscious or subconscious A lot of people who are especially influenced by or appreciate music use it as a way to chronologize their life, so a certain song can trigger past memories, good or bad associated with that period in their history. ",
